wiki.content: “Tally” The seventh track from BORN PINK is a lilting pop song with addictive rock elements throughout the song and orchestra during the rap verse. The ongoing guitar riff follow a very hip-hop pattern, making this song feel even more musically diverse. Whit self-confidence and empowering lyrics And a fierce attitude, BLACKPINK encourages us to do whatever we desire in our lives. The track is written by Nat Dunn, Danny Chung, David Phelan, Alex Oriet, Brian Lee & Soraya La Pread, and produced by Teddy Park, Nat Dunn, David Phelan, Alex Oriet, Brian Lee, Soraya La Pread & 24. The song reached the top 50 on Spotify during its release time and went viral after the group's Asia concerts tour, thanks to the great connection between fans and members during their live performance.
